  "texts": [
    "Wang et al. [2017] create a dataset of Singaporean English sentences by searching for typical Singaporean English terms in online forums.",
    "Ramponi and Casula [2023a] take a complementary approach to create a dataset of tweets in dialects of Italian along with other languages spoken in Italy (which are not necessarily derived from Italian).",
    "They use location-based search to obtain the set of tweets from different regions of interest from within Italy.",
    "Following this, they use out-of-vocabulary words to identify words that are indicative of geographical regions and, as a result, dialects.",
    "A related dataset is GeoLingIt [Ramponi and Casula 2023b]."
  ],
